snippet.textDisplay: While corporations strongly influence what laws are passed and enforced in any particular country they are also subject to those laws when they act against the political will of those controlling the levers of power. Examples would be Zuckerburg called in front of congress or Putin jailing Russian oligarchs. Tech ultimately answers to national interests. They must if they do not want to be broken up into smaller pieces or dissolved completely. The countries that control the natural resources are the countries that rule the world.
